    link: "https://www.dailymail.co.uk/money/markets/article-11133515/BUSINESS-LIVE-Cineworld-eyes-bankruptcy-Vodafone-1-8bn-unit-sale.html?ns_mchannel=rss&ns_campaign=1490&ito=1490",
